Dementro

- Dementor expands on the topics of multicast poisoning and additionally acts 
  as a rogue service provider (including CUPS RCE support)

- Overall structure is similar to Responder with more granular configuration. 
  (default is here: Dementor.toml)


Running Dementor

- With detault settings applied: 
  Dementor -I <interface>

- With default settings in analysis mode: 
  Dementor -I <interface> -A

- Automatic NTLM session downgrade (ESS): 
  Dementor -I <interface> -O NTLM.ExtendedSessionSecurity=Off

- Run current session with custom config: 
  Dementor -I <interface> --config <file.toml>

